---
code: field-order-child-first
description: Child class fields first, parent class fields last
default-enabled: false
---

field.order.with=groovy:```
    def aDefineClass = a.defineClass()
    def bDefineClass = b.defineClass()
    if(aDefineClass.qualifiedName() == bDefineClass.qualifiedName()){
        return 0
    }else if(aDefineClass.isExtend(bDefineClass.qualifiedName())){
        return -1
    }else{
        return 1
    }
```
